#: admin/views/banner.php:617
#, php-format
msgid ""
"<strong>Off by default — keep OFF for EU/EEA/UK visitors.</strong> The %1$s "
"and the %2$s identify \"X close + labelled Reject on the same banner\" as a "
"recognised dark pattern (unequal-weight dismissal paths). Safe to enable on "
