#: admin/views/cookie-policy.php:246
msgid ""
"By default the policy does <strong>not</strong> print its own title — your "
"page already has one, so a second \"Cookie Policy\" heading would duplicate "
"it. Add <code>show_title=\"true\"</code> if you embed the policy somewhere "
"without a page title and want the heading back."
msgstr ""
"Prema zadanim postavkama, pravila <strong>ne</strong> ispisuju vlastiti "
"naslov — vaša stranica već ima jedan, pa bi drugi naslov „Pravila o "
"kolačićima“ bio duplicirani sadržaj. Dodajte <code>show_title=\"true\"</"
"code> ako ugrađujete pravila na mjesto bez naslova stranice i želite naslov "
"prikazati."

#: admin/views/cookie-policy.php:248
msgid ""
"<strong>Note:</strong> the long-standing <code>[faz_cookie_policy]</code> "
"shortcode (with <code>site_name</code> / <code>contact</code> / "
"<code>show_table</code> attributes) is still supported for backward "
"compatibility. The new <code>[faz_cookie_policy_complete]</code> renders the "
"jurisdiction-aware template from the form above."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Napomena:</strong> dugogodišnji shortcode <code>[faz_cookie_policy]</"
"code> (s atributima <code>site_name</code> / <code>contact</code> / "
"<code>show_table</code>) još uvijek je podržan radi povratne "
"kompatibilnosti. Novi <code>[faz_cookie_policy_complete]</code> prikazuje "
"predložak svjestan nadležnosti iz gornjeg obrasca."

