#: admin/views/cookie-policy.php:255
msgid ""
"Page builders (Bricks, Elementor, Beaver, Divi, WPBakery): use the builder's "
"<strong>Shortcode</strong> widget/element and paste the code. Some builders "
"(Bricks in particular) skip <code>the_content()</code> entirely on pages "
"without a builder template, so the bare shortcode in the WP editor will not "
"render — use the shortcode element of your builder instead."
msgstr ""
"Graditelji stranica (Bricks, Elementor, Beaver, Divi, WPBakery): koristi "
"widget/element <strong>Kratki kod</strong> graditelja i zalijepi kod. Neki "
"graditelji (posebno Bricks) u potpunosti preskaču <code>the_content()</code> "
"na stranicama bez predloška graditelja, pa se goli kratki kod u WP uređivaču "
"neće prikazati — umjesto toga koristi element kratkog koda svog graditelja."

