msgid "Export Settings"
msgstr "Izvezi postavke"

#: admin/views/import-export.php:17
msgid ""
"Download all plugin settings, banner configuration, cookie categories, and "
"cookies as a JSON file. Consent logs, pageview data, and API keys are "
"excluded for privacy and security."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite sve postavke plugina, konfiguraciju bannera, kategorije kolačića i "
"kolačiće kao JSON datoteku. Zapisi privola, podaci o pregledima stranica i "
"API ključevi izuzeti su radi privatnosti i sigurnosti."

#: admin/views/import-export.php:27 admin/views/import-export.php:41
msgid "Import Settings"
msgstr "Uvezi postavke"

#: admin/views/import-export.php:30
msgid ""
"Upload a previously exported JSON file to restore or migrate settings. This "
"will overwrite your current plugin configuration."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite prethodno izvezenu JSON datoteku za vraćanje ili migraciju "
"postavki. Ovo će prebrisati trenutnu konfiguraciju plugina."

#: admin/views/import-export.php:32
msgid "Select JSON file"
msgstr "Odaberi JSON datoteku"

#: admin/views/import-export.php:36
msgid "Import Preview"
msgstr "Pregled uvoza"

#: admin/views/languages.php:24
msgid "Active Languages"
msgstr "Aktivni jezici"

#: admin/views/languages.php:29
msgid "Selected Languages"
msgstr "Odabrani jezici"

#: admin/views/languages.php:36
msgid "Add Language"
msgstr "Dodaj jezik"

#: admin/views/languages.php:38
msgid "Search languages..."
msgstr "Pretraži jezike..."

#. translators: %d: number of available languages
#: admin/views/languages.php:43
#, php-format
msgid "Type to search from %d available languages."
msgstr "Upišite za pretraživanje među %d dostupnih jezika."

#: admin/views/languages.php:48
msgid "Default Language"
msgstr "Zadani jezik"

#: admin/views/languages.php:52
msgid ""
"The language used when the visitor's browser language does not match any of "
"the active languages above."
msgstr ""
"Jezik koji se koristi kada jezik preglednika posjetitelja ne odgovara "
"nijednom od gore aktivnih jezika."

#: admin/views/languages.php:56
msgid "Save Languages"
msgstr "Spremi jezike"

#: admin/views/settings.php:14
msgid "Banner Control"
msgstr "Kontrola bannera"

#: admin/views/settings.php:23
msgid ""
"When disabled, the cookie consent banner will not appear on your site and no "
"scripts will be blocked."
msgstr ""
"Kada je onemogućeno, banner za privolu kolačića neće se prikazivati na vašoj "
"stranici i skripte se neće blokirati."

#: admin/views/settings.php:26
msgid "Excluded Pages"
msgstr "Izuzete stranice"

#: admin/views/settings.php:27
msgid "One per line: page ID or URL pattern like /privacy/*"
msgstr "Jedan unos po retku: ID stranice ili URL obrazac poput /privacy/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:28
msgid "Enter page IDs or URL patterns, one per line."
msgstr "Unesite ID-jeve stranica ili URL obrasce, jedan po retku."

#: admin/views/settings.php:34
msgid "Hide banner from search engine bots"
msgstr "Sakrij banner od robota tražilica"

#: admin/views/settings.php:36
msgid ""
"Automatically detects search engine crawlers (Googlebot, Bingbot, etc.) and "
"skips the banner for them. Improves SEO by serving cleaner HTML to crawlers."
msgstr ""
"Automatski detektira robote tražilica (Googlebot, Bingbot itd.) i preskače "
"banner za njih. Poboljšava SEO serviranjem čišćeg HTML-a robotima."

#: admin/views/settings.php:42
msgid "Push consent events to GTM Data Layer"
msgstr "Šalji događaje privole u GTM Data Layer"

#: admin/views/settings.php:44
msgid ""
"Pushes a faz_consent_update event with per-category granted/denied values to "
"window.dataLayer after each consent action. Enable if you use Google Tag "
"Manager."
msgstr ""
"Šalje događaj faz_consent_update s vrijednostima granted/denied po "
"kategoriji u window.dataLayer nakon svake radnje privole. Omogućite ako "
"koristite Google Tag Manager."

#: admin/views/settings.php:50
msgid "Ad-blocker compatibility mode"
msgstr "Način kompatibilnosti s blokatorima oglasa"

#: admin/views/settings.php:52
msgid ""
"Uses generic script handle names to prevent ad blockers from blocking the "
"cookie banner. Enable if visitors report the banner not appearing."
msgstr ""
"Koristi generičke nazive handleova skripti kako bi spriječio blokatore "
"oglasa da blokiraju banner za kolačiće. Omogućite ako posjetitelji "
"prijavljuju da se banner ne prikazuje."

#: admin/views/settings.php:58
msgid "Enable per-service consent"
msgstr "Omogući privolu po usluzi"

#: admin/views/settings.php:60
msgid ""
"When enabled, visitors can accept or reject individual services (e.g., "
"Google Analytics, YouTube) instead of entire categories. Services detected "
"by the scanner are shown immediately, and embedded providers blocked at "
"runtime are revealed when the browser sees them on the page. This keeps the "
"preference center present-aware but makes it more complex."
msgstr ""
"Kada je omogućeno, posjetitelji mogu prihvatiti ili odbiti pojedinačne "
"usluge (npr. Google Analytics, YouTube) umjesto cijelih kategorija. Usluge "
"koje otkrije skener prikazuju se odmah, a ugrađeni pružatelji blokirani u "
"runtimeu otkrivaju se kada ih preglednik vidi na stranici. Time centar "
"postavki ostaje svjestan stvarne prisutnosti usluga, ali postaje složeniji."

#: admin/views/settings.php:66
msgid "Enable per-cookie consent"
msgstr "Omogući privolu po kolačiću"

#: admin/views/settings.php:68
msgid ""
"Requires per-service consent. Adds a nested row for each cookie a service "
"declares. First-party cookies that the site can write are enforced by client "
"cleanup and the server-side shredder. Cookies set by embedded third-party "
"services on their own domains (for example YouTube, Vimeo, Maps, social "
"embeds) cannot be deleted individually by this site; those rows are shown as "
"disabled and are controlled by allowing or blocking the whole embed."
msgstr ""
"Zahtijeva privolu po usluzi. Dodaje ugniježđeni redak za svaki kolačić koji "
"usluga deklarira. First-party kolačići koje web-mjesto može zapisati provode "
"se klijentskim čišćenjem i poslužiteljskim shredderom. Kolačiće koje "
"ugrađene usluge trećih strana postavljaju na vlastitim domenama (na primjer "
"YouTube, Vimeo, Maps, društveni embedovi) ovo web-mjesto ne može pojedinačno "
"izbrisati; ti se redci prikazuju kao onemogućeni i kontroliraju se "
"dopuštanjem ili blokiranjem cijelog embeda."

#: admin/views/settings.php:74
msgid "Share consent across subdomains"
msgstr "Dijeli privolu među poddomenama"

#: admin/views/settings.php:76
msgid ""
"Scope the consent cookie to your registrable domain (e.g. .example.com) so "
"it is shared across www, shop, app, etc. Recommended only when all "
"subdomains belong to you and are covered by the same privacy policy. Public-"
"suffix-aware for multi-level TLDs (.co.uk, .com.au)."
msgstr ""
"Ogranite kolačić privole na svoju registrabilnu domenu (npr. .example.com) "
"kako bi se dijelio na www, shop, app itd. Preporučuje se samo kada svi "
"poddomeni pripadaju vama i pokriveni su istom politikom privatnosti. "
"Podržava javne sufikse za višerazinske TLD-ove (.co.uk, .com.au)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:82
#, fuzzy
msgid "Cache compatibility mode"
msgstr "Način kompatibilnosti s blokatorima oglasa"

#: admin/views/settings.php:84
msgid ""
"Keep the page fully cacheable by LiteSpeed, QUIC.cloud, Varnish, Nginx "
"FastCGI or WP Rocket. The plugin stops emitting <code>no-cache</code>/"
"<code>no-store</code> headers and the <code>DONOTCACHEPAGE</code> constant "
"for anonymous visitors, so the static HTML is cached and the banner runs "
"entirely client-side from the consent cookie. <strong>Only enable this if "
"your banner output does NOT vary by visitor country.</strong> With IAB TCF, "
"geo-targeting, country-targeted banners or runtime geo-routing active, the "
"same cached HTML would be served to every region (e.g. an EU TCF "
"<code>gdprApplies=true</code> page reaching a US visitor) — keep this OFF in "
"that case, or vary the cache by country at the CDN."
msgstr ""

#: admin/views/settings.php:91 admin/views/system-status.php:88
msgid "Cross-Domain Consent"
msgstr "Privola između domena"

#: admin/views/settings.php:98
msgid "Enable cross-domain consent forwarding"
msgstr "Omogući prosljeđivanje privole između domena"

#: admin/views/settings.php:100
msgid ""
"Share consent choices across multiple domains. When a visitor accepts or "
"rejects cookies on one domain, the same choice is forwarded to all "
"configured target domains via secure postMessage."
msgstr ""
"Dijelite odabire privole između više domena. Kada posjetitelj prihvati ili "
"odbije kolačiće na jednoj domeni, isti odabir prosljeđuje se svim "
"konfiguriranim ciljnim domenama putem sigurnog postMessage mehanizma."

#: admin/views/settings.php:103
msgid "Target Domains"
msgstr "Ciljne domene"

#: admin/views/settings.php:104
msgid "One per line: https://shop.example.com"
msgstr "Jedna po retku: https://shop.example.com"

#: admin/views/settings.php:105
msgid ""
"Full URLs of other sites that should receive consent state. Each site must "
"also have FAZ Cookie Manager installed. One URL per line."
msgstr ""
"Puni URL-ovi drugih stranica koje trebaju primiti stanje privole. Svaka "
"stranica također mora imati instaliran FAZ Cookie Manager. Jedan URL po "
"retku."

#: admin/views/settings.php:112 admin/views/system-status.php:80
msgid "Pageview Tracking"
msgstr "Praćenje pregleda stranica"

#: admin/views/settings.php:119
msgid "Enable pageview and banner interaction tracking"
msgstr "Omogući praćenje pregleda stranica i interakcija s bannerom"

#: admin/views/settings.php:121
msgid ""
"Tracks pageviews and banner interactions (accept, reject, settings) for the "
"dashboard analytics. Data is aggregate-only: it sends the page URL and title "
"with no per-visitor identifier or cookie, so the events cannot be linked "
"across pages or sessions. Counts are stored first-party in your own "
"database. Disable for stricter compliance."
msgstr ""
"Prati preglede stranica i interakcije s bannerom (prihvaćanje, odbijanje, "
"postavke) za analitiku nadzorne ploče. Podaci su isključivo skupni: šalju se "
"samo URL i naslov stranice, bez identifikatora pojedinog posjetitelja ili "
"kolačića, pa se događaji ne mogu povezivati među stranicama ili sesijama. "
"Brojevi se pohranjuju kao podaci prve strane u vašoj vlastitoj bazi "
"podataka. Onemogućite za strožu usklađenost."

#: admin/views/settings.php:128
msgid "Script Blocking"
msgstr "Blokiranje skripti"

#: admin/views/settings.php:132
msgid "Pages Excluded from Script Blocking"
msgstr "Stranice izuzete iz blokiranja skripti"

#: admin/views/settings.php:133
msgid "One per line: /checkout/* or /cart/*"
msgstr "Jedan unos po retku: /checkout/* ili /cart/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:134
msgid ""
"URL patterns where script blocking is disabled (banner still shows). One per "
"line, supports wildcards (e.g. <code>/checkout/*</code>)."
msgstr ""
"URL obrasci na kojima je blokiranje skripti onemogućeno (banner se i dalje "
"prikazuje). Jedan po retku, podržava zamjenske znakove (npr. <code>/checkout/"
"*</code>)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:137
msgid "Script Blocking Exceptions"
msgstr "Iznimke blokiranja skripti"

#: admin/views/settings.php:138
msgid "One per line: googleapis.com/youtube/v3, recaptcha, my-inline-script-id"
msgstr ""
"Jedan po retku: googleapis.com/youtube/v3, recaptcha, my-inline-script-id"

#: admin/views/settings.php:139
msgid ""
"Scripts that should never be blocked, even before consent. One per line. "
"Accepts three types of pattern:<br>- <strong>URL fragment</strong> (contains "
"<code>.</code> or <code>/</code>): matched against the script's <code>src</"
"code> or related URL attribute, e.g. <code>googleapis.com/youtube/v3</code>."
"<br>- <strong>Script ID</strong> (no dots/slashes): matched against the "
"<code>id</code> attribute of the script tag, e.g. <code>my-product-form-"
"data</code>.<br>- <strong>CSS class</strong> (no dots/slashes): matched "
"against the script's <code>class</code> attribute, e.g. <code>recaptcha</"
"code>.<br>These exceptions bypass blocking entirely. Use them only for "
"scripts that genuinely do not set tracking cookies. <strong>Be specific</"
"strong> to avoid accidentally unblocking trackers.<br><strong>Tip:</strong> "
"You can also add <code>class=\"faz-skip\"</code> directly to any script tag "
"to exclude it without adding anything here — no configuration needed."
msgstr ""
"Skripte koje nikada ne smiju biti blokirane, čak ni prije privole. Jedna po "
"retku. Prihvaća tri vrste uzoraka:<br>- <strong>Fragment URL-a</strong> "
"(sadrži <code>.</code> ili <code>/</code>): usporeduje se s atributom "
"<code>src</code> skripte ili srodnim URL-om, npr. <code>googleapis.com/"
"youtube/v3</code>.<br>- <strong>ID skripte</strong> (bez točaka/kosačica): "
"usporeduje se s atributom <code>id</code> oznake skripte, npr. <code>my-"
"product-form-data</code>.<br>- <strong>CSS klasa</strong> (bez točaka/"
"kosačica): usporeduje se s atributom <code>class</code> skripte, npr. "
"<code>recaptcha</code>.<br>Ove iznimke u potpunosti zaobilaze blokiranje. "
"Koristite ih samo za skripte koje zaista ne postavljaju kolačiće za "
"praćenje. <strong>Budite precizni</strong> kako biste izbjegli slučajno "
"deblokiranje pračitelja.<br><strong>Savjet:</strong> možete i dodati "
"<code>class=\"faz-skip\"</code> izravno bilo kojoj oznaci skripte kako biste "
"je isključili bez dodavanja ičega ovdje — nije potrebna nikakva "
"konfiguracija."

#: admin/views/settings.php:145
msgid "Advanced inline CSS URL blocking"
msgstr ""

#: admin/views/settings.php:147
msgid ""
"Optional high-coverage mode for CSS-based third-party loads. The default "
"blocker already handles server-rendered <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> tags and "
"direct <code>HTMLStyleElement</code> updates. Enable this only if you have "
"confirmed that a theme, page builder, or CSS-in-JS library injects blocked "
"<code>url()</code> or <code>@import</code> rules through broader runtime "
"channels such as <code>Element.innerHTML</code>, <code>insertAdjacentHTML</"
"code>, <code>CharacterData</code> edits inside a style tag, or Constructable "
"Stylesheets. This strengthens pre-consent blocking but hooks global browser "
"APIs and may affect builders, editors, icon fonts, or CSS-in-JS libraries. "
"Test the site before enabling in production."
msgstr ""

#: admin/views/settings.php:161
msgid "Enable consent logging"
msgstr "Omogući bilježenje privole"

#: admin/views/settings.php:163
msgid ""
"Records each visitor's consent choice (accepted, rejected, or partial) for "
"GDPR accountability. Required by Art. 7(1) GDPR to demonstrate that consent "
"was given."
msgstr ""
"Bilježi svaki odabir privole posjetitelja (prihvaćeno, odbijeno ili "
"djelomično) za GDPR odgovornost. Potrebno prema čl. 7. st. 1. GDPR-a za "
"dokazivanje da je privola dana."

#: admin/views/settings.php:166
msgid "Retention Period (months)"
msgstr "Razdoblje zadržavanja (mjeseci)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:168
msgid ""
"How long consent records are kept before automatic deletion. Most DPAs "
"recommend 12 months. Logs older than this period are purged daily."
msgstr ""
"Koliko dugo se zapisi privola čuvaju prije automatskog brisanja. Većina "
"nadzornih tijela preporučuje 12 mjeseci. Zapisi stariji od tog razdoblja "
"brišu se svakodnevno."

#: admin/views/settings.php:175
msgid "Scanner"
msgstr "Skener"

#: admin/views/settings.php:179
msgid "Max Pages to Scan"
msgstr "Maks. broj stranica za skeniranje"

#: admin/views/settings.php:181
msgid ""
"Maximum number of pages the cookie scanner will crawl. Higher values find "
"more cookies but take longer. 100 pages is sufficient for most sites."
msgstr ""
"Maksimalan broj stranica koje će skener kolačića obići. Veće vrijednosti "
"pronalaze više kolačića, ali traju dulje. 100 stranica dovoljno je za većinu "
"web-stranica."

#: admin/views/settings.php:187
msgid "Scanner Debug Mode"
msgstr "Način otklanjanja pogrešaka skenera"

#: admin/views/settings.php:189
msgid ""
"When enabled, the scanner logs every categorization decision. Download logs "
"from the Cookies page."
msgstr ""
"Kada je omogućeno, skener bilježi svaku odluku o kategorizaciji. Preuzmite "
"zapisnike sa stranice Kolačići."

#: admin/views/settings.php:196
msgid "Automatic Scanning"
msgstr "Automatsko skeniranje"

#: admin/views/settings.php:203
msgid "Enable automatic cookie scanning"
msgstr "Omogući automatsko skeniranje kolačića"

#: admin/views/settings.php:205
msgid ""
"Automatically scan your site for new cookies on a schedule. You will receive "
"an email notification if new uncategorized cookies are found."
msgstr ""
"Automatski skenirajte svoju stranicu za nove kolačiće prema rasporedu. "
"Primit ćete e-mail obavijest ako se pronađu novi nekategorizirani kolačići."

#: admin/views/settings.php:208
msgid "Scan Frequency"
msgstr "Učestalost skeniranja"

#: admin/views/settings.php:210
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "Dnevno"

#: admin/views/settings.php:211 includes/class-activator.php:200
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "Tjedno"

#: admin/views/settings.php:212
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Mjesečno"

#: admin/views/settings.php:214
msgid ""
"How often the scanner runs automatically. Weekly is recommended for most "
"sites."
msgstr ""
"Koliko često se skener automatski pokreće. Tjedno je preporučeno za većinu "
"stranica."

#: admin/views/settings.php:221
msgid "Microsoft Consent APIs"
msgstr "Microsoft Consent API-ji"

#: admin/views/settings.php:228
msgid "Microsoft UET Consent Mode"
msgstr "Microsoft UET Consent Mode"

#: admin/views/settings.php:230
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Advertising (Bing Ads) via the UET tag. "
"Enable if you use Microsoft Advertising and need to respect consent for ad "
"tracking."
msgstr ""
"Signalizira status privole Microsoft Advertisingu (Bing Ads) putem UET taga. "
"Omogućite ako koristite Microsoft Advertising i trebate poštovati privolu za "
"praćenje oglasa."

#: admin/views/settings.php:236
msgid "Microsoft Clarity Consent API"
msgstr "Microsoft Clarity Consent API"

#: admin/views/settings.php:238
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Clarity (heatmaps and session "
"recordings). Enable if you use Clarity and want it to pause tracking until "
"consent is given."
msgstr ""
"Signalizira status privole Microsoft Clarityju (heatmapovi i snimke sesija). "
"Omogućite ako koristite Clarity i želite pauzirati praćenje dok privola nije "
"dana."

#: admin/views/settings.php:245
msgid "Age Verification"
msgstr "Provjera dobi"

#: admin/views/settings.php:252
msgid "Require age verification for consent"
msgstr "Zahtijevaj provjeru dobi za privolu"

#: admin/views/settings.php:254
msgid ""
"Under GDPR Art. 8, children below the minimum age cannot give valid consent "
"for data processing. When enabled, visitors must confirm they meet the "
"minimum age before accepting optional cookies."
msgstr ""
"Prema čl. 8. GDPR-a, djeca ispod minimalne dobi ne mogu dati valjanu privolu "
"za obradu podataka. Kada je omogućeno, posjetitelji moraju potvrditi da "
"zadovoljavaju minimalnu dob prije prihvaćanja opcionalnih kolačića."

#: admin/views/settings.php:257
msgid "Minimum Age"
msgstr "Minimalna dob"

#: admin/views/settings.php:259
msgid ""
"GDPR default is 16. Some EU member states allow 13-15. Check your local law."
msgstr ""
"Zadana vrijednost GDPR-a je 16. Neke države članice EU-a dopuštaju 13–15. "
"Provjerite lokalni zakon."

#: admin/views/settings.php:266
msgid "IAB TCF"
msgstr "IAB TCF"

#: admin/views/settings.php:273
msgid "Enable IAB TCF v2.3"
msgstr "Omogući IAB TCF v2.3"

#: admin/views/settings.php:275
msgid ""
"Enables the IAB Transparency & Consent Framework. Required if you work with "
"ad-tech vendors that need a standardised TC String for programmatic "
"advertising in the EU."
msgstr ""
"Omogućuje IAB Transparency & Consent Framework. Potrebno ako radite s ad-"
"tech dobavljačima kojima je potreban standardizirani TC String za "
"programatsko oglašavanje u EU-u."

#: admin/views/settings.php:278
msgid "Publisher Country Code"
msgstr "Kod države izdavača"

#: admin/views/settings.php:280
msgid ""
"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 code of the publisher's country (e.g. IT, DE, FR). Used "
"in the TCF consent string."
msgstr ""
"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 kod države izdavača (npr. IT, DE, FR). Koristi se u TCF "
"stringu privole."

#: admin/views/settings.php:283
msgid "CMP ID"
msgstr "CMP ID"

#: admin/views/settings.php:285
msgid ""
"Your registered IAB CMP ID (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IAB CMP List</a>). With "
"ID&nbsp;0 the banner and cookie blocking work normally, but ad-tech vendors "
"will ignore the TC String. Google Consent Mode v2 works regardless of CMP "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"Vaš registrirani IAB CMP ID (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IAB CMP popis</a>). S ID-"
"jem&nbsp;0 banner i blokiranje kolačića rade normalno, ali ad-tech "
"dobavljači ignorirat će TC String. Google Consent Mode v2 radi neovisno o "
"CMP registraciji."

#: admin/views/settings.php:291
msgid "Purpose One Treatment"
msgstr "Purpose One Treatment"

#: admin/views/settings.php:293
msgid ""
"Set to true if Purpose 1 consent was NOT disclosed (e.g. publisher in a "
"country where Purpose 1 is not required)."
msgstr ""
"Postavite na true ako privola za Purpose 1 NIJE objavljena (npr. izdavač u "
"zemlji u kojoj Purpose 1 nije potreban)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:297
msgid "Loading GVL status..."
msgstr "Učitavanje GVL statusa..."

#: admin/views/settings.php:306 admin/views/system-status.php:82
msgid "Geo-Targeting"
msgstr "Geo-ciljanje"

#: admin/views/settings.php:313
msgid "Enable geo-targeted banner display"
msgstr "Omogući geo-ciljani prikaz bannera"

#: admin/views/settings.php:315
msgid ""
"Show the cookie banner only to visitors from specific regions. Requires a "
"MaxMind GeoLite2 database (configured below) or Cloudflare CF-IPCountry "
"header."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži banner za kolačiće samo posjetiteljima iz određenih regija. "
"Zahtijeva MaxMind GeoLite2 bazu podataka (konfiguriranu ispod) ili "
"Cloudflare CF-IPCountry zaglavlje."

#: admin/views/settings.php:318
msgid "Target Regions"
msgstr "Ciljne regije"

#: admin/views/settings.php:322
msgid "EU / EEA"
msgstr "EU / EGP"

#: admin/views/settings.php:323
msgid "United Kingdom"
msgstr "Ujedinjeno Kraljevstvo"

#: admin/views/settings.php:324
msgid "United States"
msgstr "Sjedinjene Američke Države"

