#: admin/views/settings.php:354
msgid "GeoIP Database (MaxMind GeoLite2)"
msgstr "GeoIP baza podataka (MaxMind GeoLite2)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:358
msgid ""
"Geo-targeting requires a MaxMind GeoLite2 database. <a href=\"https://"
"www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get "
"a free license key</a>."
msgstr ""
"Geociljanje zahtijeva MaxMind GeoLite2 bazu podataka. <a href=\"https://"
"www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener\">Nabavite besplatni licencni ključ</a>."

#: admin/views/settings.php:361
msgid "Database edition"
msgstr "Izdanje baze podataka"

#: admin/views/settings.php:363
msgid "Country &#8212; country-level only (recommended)"
msgstr "Country &#8212; samo na razini države (preporučeno)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:364
msgid "City &#8212; adds region / state detection"
msgstr "City &#8212; dodaje otkrivanje regije/savezne države"

#: admin/views/settings.php:367
msgid ""
"<strong>Country</strong> (~10 MB) resolves the visitor&#8217;s country only "
"&#8212; enough for country-based banner targeting and most per-jurisdiction "
"rules. <strong>City</strong> (~60&#8211;110 MB) additionally resolves the "
"region / province / state, which a few rules need: sub-national regimes such "
"as <em>Quebec Law 25</em> apply only inside one region of a country, so "
"without City (or a Cloudflare <code>CF-Region-Code</code> header) the plugin "
"can only see &#8220;Canada&#8221; and cannot route that visitor to the "
"Quebec ruleset. Choose City only if you rely on region-level routing &#8212; "
"it is a much larger download. Changing this and clicking &#8220;Update "
"Database&#8221; replaces the installed database."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Country</strong> (~10 MB) razlučuje samo državu posjetitelja &#8212; "
"dovoljno za ciljanje banera po državi i većinu pravila po jurisdikciji. "
"<strong>City</strong> (~60&#8211;110 MB) dodatno razlučuje regiju / "
"pokrajinu / saveznu državu, što je potrebno za nekoliko pravila: "
"subnacionalni režimi poput <em>Zakona 25 iz Quebeca</em> primjenjuju se samo "
"unutar jedne regije države, pa bez Cityja (ili Cloudflareova zaglavlja "
"<code>CF-Region-Code</code>) dodatak vidi samo &#8220;Kanadu&#8221; i ne "
"može usmjeriti tog posjetitelja na ruleset Quebeca. Odaberite City samo ako "
"se oslanjate na usmjeravanje na razini regije &#8212; riječ je o znatno "
"većem preuzimanju. Promjena ove postavke i klik na &#8220;Ažuriraj bazu "
"podataka&#8221; zamjenjuje instaliranu bazu."

#: admin/views/settings.php:371
msgid "MaxMind License Key"
msgstr "MaxMind licencni ključ"

#: admin/views/settings.php:372
msgid "Enter your MaxMind license key"
msgstr "Unesite svoj MaxMind licencni ključ"

#: admin/views/settings.php:376
msgid "Update Database"
msgstr "Ažuriraj bazu podataka"

#: admin/views/settings.php:382
msgid "Data Management"
msgstr "Upravljanje podacima"

#: admin/views/settings.php:389
msgid "Remove all data on uninstall"
msgstr "Ukloni sve podatke pri deinstalaciji"

#: admin/views/settings.php:391
msgid ""
"When enabled, deleting the plugin will permanently remove ALL data: cookies, "
"categories, consent logs, pageviews, banner settings, and scan history. Keep "
"this OFF if you plan to reinstall or update the plugin."
msgstr ""
"Kada je omogućeno, brisanje dodatka trajno će ukloniti SVE podatke: "
"kolačiće, kategorije, zapisnike pristanka, preglede stranica, postavke "
"bannera i povijest skeniranja. Ostavite ovo ISKLJUČENO ako planirate "
"reinstalirati ili ažurirati dodatak."

#: admin/views/settings.php:399
msgid "Paid Memberships Pro integration"
msgstr "Integracija Paid Memberships Pro"

#: admin/views/settings.php:403
msgid ""
"Implement a \"Pay-or-Accept\" model: logged-in members on selected PMP "
"levels skip the cookie banner and have consent <strong>programmatically "
"recorded as granted for all categories</strong> via a server-side cookie. "
"Marketing, analytics, functional and other non-necessary scripts will run "
"for them without an explicit banner interaction. Free visitors continue to "
"see the standard banner and consent flow."
msgstr ""
"Implementirajte model \"Plati ili Prihvati\": prijavljeni članovi na "
"odabranim PMP razinama preskakuju banner za kolačiće i dobivaju pristanak "
"<strong>programski zabilježen kao odobren za sve kategorije</strong> putem "
"kolačića na strani poslužitelja. Marketinške, analitičke, funkcionalne i "
"druge neobvezne skripte pokreću se za njih bez izričite interakcije s "
"bannerom. Besplatni posjetitelji nastavljaju vidjeti standardni banner i "
"tijek pristanka."

#: admin/views/settings.php:406
msgid "Legal note:"
msgstr "Pravna napomena:"

#: admin/views/settings.php:407
msgid ""
"Because this option grants consent on behalf of the member (it does not "
"merely hide the banner), you must disclose it clearly in your Terms of "
"Service, Privacy Policy, and at the point of subscription so the membership "
"fee is understood as a genuine alternative to giving consent (EDPB Opinion "
"08/2024). Members must remain able to revoke or adjust their consent at any "
"time via the standard revisit widget."
msgstr ""
"Budući da ova opcija daje suglasnost u ime člana (ne skriva samo banner), "
"morate to jasno objaviti u Uvjetima korištenja, Politici privatnosti i u "
"trenutku pretplate kako bi se članarina razumjela kao prava alternativa "
"davanju suglasnosti (Mišljenje EDPB-a 08/2024). Članovi moraju uvijek moći "
"opozvati ili prilagoditi svoju suglasnost putem standardnog widgeta ponovnog "
"posjeta."

#: admin/views/settings.php:413
msgid "Enable PMP integration"
msgstr "Omogući PMP integraciju"

#: admin/views/settings.php:417
msgid "Exempt membership level IDs"
msgstr "ID-ovi razina članstva koji su izuzeti"

#: admin/views/settings.php:418
msgid "e.g. 2, 3, 5"
msgstr "npr. 2, 3, 5"

#: admin/views/settings.php:420
msgid ""
"Comma-separated PMP level IDs whose members should be exempted. Find level "
"IDs in <strong>Memberships → Settings → Levels</strong>. Leave empty to "
"disable exemption."
msgstr ""
"ID-ovi PMP razina odvojeni zarezima čiji bi članovi trebali biti izuzeti. ID-"
"ove razina pronađite u <strong>Memberships → Settings → Levels</strong>. "
"Ostavite prazno za onemogućavanje izuzeća."

#: admin/views/settings.php:429
msgid "Force re-consent"
msgstr "Prisilno zatražiti novi pristanak"

#: admin/views/settings.php:433
msgid ""
"Show the cookie banner again to all returning visitors. Useful when you "
"change which cookies or services are used on your site (e.g. new AdSense "
"tags, added analytics) and want prior visitors to renew their consent before "
"those services run."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži banner s kolačićima ponovo svim povratnim posjetiteljima. Korisno "
"kada promijenite koji se kolačići ili usluge koriste na vašoj web-stranici "
"(npr. novi AdSense oznake, dodana analitika) i želite da prethodni "
"posjetitelji obnove svoju privolu prije nego što te usluge budu pokrenute."

#: admin/views/settings.php:436
msgid "Current consent revision"
msgstr "Trenutna revizija pristanka"

#: admin/views/settings.php:440
msgid "Invalidate all consents"
msgstr "Poništi sve pristanke"

#: admin/views/settings.php:443
msgid ""
"Visitors whose stored consent has a lower revision will see the banner again "
"on their next visit. This does not affect the current page load."
msgstr ""
"Posjetitelji čija pohranjena suglasnost ima nižu reviziju vidjet æe banner "
"ponovo pri sljedećem posjetu. Ovo ne utječe na trenutno učitavanje stranice."

